          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "One that would express Him and fulfill His plan."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Isaac from his father did inherit all:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sonship’s full enjoyment, blessing of God’s call."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though all things receiving, incomplete was he;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lacking transformation and maturity."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our Lord God Jehovah called a corporate man,"
